146
00:08:38.601 --> 00:08:39.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We’ve gotta get home right away.

147
00:08:39.977 --> 00:08:42.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
