151
00:08:51.447 --> 00:08:54.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Is that so? A group exhibition?

152
00:08:54.492 --> 00:08:56.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
