163
00:09:20.977 --> 00:09:24.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I feel an even stronger sense</i>
<i>that they’re leaving me behind.</i>

164
00:09:28.401 --> 00:09:31.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
