165
00:09:33.781 --> 00:09:34.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hello, Nana here.

166
00:09:34.991 --> 00:09:36.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, Nana?

167
00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:39.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Good job with the concert.
