168
00:09:40.121 --> 00:09:41.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We got a ride home.

169
00:09:41.998 --> 00:09:44.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What about you guys, Nana?
What time can you get here?

170
00:09:44.250 --> 00:09:47.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sorry. It doesn’t look like
we’re gonna be able to make it.

171
00:09:47.128 --> 00:09:50.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We’ve been invited to have dinner
with the guy from Gaia.

172
00:09:50.548 --> 00:09:52.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I imagine we’ll be pretty late.

173
00:09:55.011 --> 00:09:57.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Did you already make preparations
for our after-party?

174
00:09:58.055 --> 00:10:00.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, not yet! We just got home!

175
00:10:01.767 --> 00:10:03.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I’m really sorry.</i>

176
00:10:03.519 --> 00:10:05.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Not to worry.</i>

177
00:10:05.438 --> 00:10:08.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It’s okay, don’t worry about us. Go.

178
00:10:08.899 --> 00:10:11.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>This kinda stuff happens often.</i>

179
00:10:11.527 --> 00:10:15.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I’m working tomorrow evening,</i>
<i>but I’ll stop by during the day.</i>

180
00:10:15.990 --> 00:10:18.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, but I have work
from the morning tomorrow.

181
00:10:18.993 --> 00:10:20.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What about Misato? Let me talk to her.</i>

182
00:10:22.580 --> 00:10:23.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It’s Nana.

183
00:10:24.665 --> 00:10:25.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hello?

184
00:10:26.542 --> 00:10:29.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes. Nana, it was an awesome performance.

185
00:10:31.005 --> 00:10:32.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

186
00:10:32.715 --> 00:10:34.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh? Is that so?

187
00:10:35.468 --> 00:10:38.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No, let’s hope they bring up
the subject of a contract.

188
00:10:39.221 --> 00:10:41.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? Tomorrow?

189
00:10:42.016 --> 00:10:43.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What about me?</i>

190
00:10:43.726 --> 00:10:46.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes, I’ll be waiting for you at home.

191
00:10:47.855 --> 00:10:50.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Hey, Nana, what about me?</i>

192
00:10:57.239 --> 00:10:59.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Nana, Mr. Kawano’s
called for a taxi. Let's go.

193
00:11:00.618 --> 00:11:02.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They’re waiting in the street…

194
00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:04.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oops. Sorry, you’re on the phone.

195
00:11:04.705 --> 00:11:07.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorry, Misato, I have to go now.

196
00:11:07.416 --> 00:11:08.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Say bye to Hachiko for me, okay?

197
00:11:09.669 --> 00:11:12.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? Oh, go ahead.

198
00:11:12.546 --> 00:11:16.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Feel free to stay in my room.
The room’s not locked.

199
00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:18.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mm-hmm. Bye.

200
00:11:19.136 --> 00:11:21.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Was that Misato? What about Hachi?

201
00:11:21.972 --> 00:11:23.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She said not to worry and go.

202
00:11:24.850 --> 00:11:28.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Misato and Hachiko should come
and join us for sushi.

203
00:11:28.771 --> 00:11:30.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You idiot. Let’s go.

204
00:11:31.399 --> 00:11:32.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Idiot?

205
00:11:36.195 --> 00:11:37.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Good job.

206
00:11:37.363 --> 00:11:38.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh!

207
00:11:38.364 --> 00:11:40.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nana!

208
00:11:44.203 --> 00:11:47.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I live, encouraged by the songs you sing.</i>

209
00:11:49.375 --> 00:11:51.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It’s only natural for Nana</i>
<i>to treat Misato,</i>

210
00:11:51.752 --> 00:11:54.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>who pursues Nana with passion</i>

211
00:11:54.088 --> 00:11:56.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>and makes the effort to come</i>
<i>all the way to Tokyo for every concert,</i>

212
00:11:56.340 --> 00:11:59.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>more importantly than she treats me.</i>

213
00:11:59.677 --> 00:12:02.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It’s only natural for Nana to place</i>
<i>a higher priority on talks</i>

214
00:12:02.179 --> 00:12:05.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>with a record label than any promise</i>
<i>she made with me.</i>

215
00:12:05.933 --> 00:12:07.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>And it’s also only natural that</i>

216
00:12:08.185 --> 00:12:10.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>she would choose to be with Ren</i>
<i>than live with me.</i>

217
00:12:11.522 --> 00:12:13.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It all makes sense.</i>

218
00:12:14.942 --> 00:12:20.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>But if that’s the case…</i>
<i>she no longer needs me.</i>

219
00:12:20.448 --> 00:12:25.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It’s such a shame, Ms. Hachiko,
after making all this food.

220
00:12:25.911 --> 00:12:26.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

221
00:12:27.788 --> 00:12:29.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, right!

222
00:12:29.665 --> 00:12:31.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It can’t be helped,
given the circumstances.

223
00:12:31.125 --> 00:12:33.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don’t feel pressured into eating more
than you want, Misato.

224
00:12:33.836 --> 00:12:36.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But everything’s so delicious.
It would be hard not to overeat.

225
00:12:36.922 --> 00:12:41.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You’re a very good cook,
Ms. Hachiko. I’m impressed.

226
00:12:43.387 --> 00:12:46.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Misato is such a nice girl.</i>

227
00:12:46.849 --> 00:12:49.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>She is so much in love with Nana</i>

228
00:12:49.727 --> 00:12:53.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>yet will never show hostile sentiments</i>
<i>to those around her.</i>

229
00:12:53.147 --> 00:12:56.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>And she was honestly happy</i>
<i>about Nana and Ren.</i>

230
00:12:56.567 --> 00:12:58.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>She’s a really cute, good girl,</i>

231
00:12:59.028 --> 00:13:03.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>which exhausts me all the more</i>
<i>with my tendency to be cynical.</i>

232
00:13:03.949 --> 00:13:07.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I wonder if we can get along</i>
<i>for a full month.</i>

