00:13:14.376 --> 00:13:16.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
A FRIEND WILL BE STAYING WITH ME
DURING SUMMER VACATION,

237
00:13:16.795 --> 00:13:18.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
SO DON'T COME BY MY PLACE, OKAY?
NANA

238
00:13:18.881 --> 00:13:24.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>This is like telling him that I can’t</i>
<i>see him until summer vacation is over.</i>

239
00:13:24.220 --> 00:13:25.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Well, I guess that’s fine.</i>

240
00:13:25.596 --> 00:13:27.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Since being with him,</i>

241
00:13:27.139 --> 00:13:28.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I’ve never been sure whether</i>
<i>or not I’ll ever see him again anyway.</i>

242
00:13:30.351 --> 00:13:33.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I ended up not seeing Nobu again as well.</i>

243
00:13:33.812 --> 00:13:37.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>And while he was on stage,</i>
<i>I purposely tried not to look over to him.</i>

244
00:13:46.784 --> 00:13:47.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Nana…</i>

245
00:13:55.668 --> 00:13:57.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>This isn’t good. What should I do?</i>

246
00:13:58.462 --> 00:14:00.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I’m feeling so lonely.</i>

247
00:14:08.514 --> 00:14:10.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Is your friend a woman?

248
00:14:13.769 --> 00:14:14.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Of course!

249
00:14:14.937 --> 00:14:17.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Really? Then that’s fine. Good night.

250
00:14:32.037 --> 00:14:33.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

251
00:14:33.122 --> 00:14:34.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Takumi…</i>

252
00:14:36.041 --> 00:14:37.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I wanna see you.

253
00:14:42.298 --> 00:14:45.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, Ms. Hachiko,
thank you for letting me take a bath.

254
00:14:45.426 --> 00:14:48.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I’m sorry, Misato.
I’m going out for a bit.

255
00:14:48.512 --> 00:14:51.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? At this hour? Did something happen?

256
00:14:51.807 --> 00:14:55.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
