from there tomorrow.

258
00:14:57.563 --> 00:14:58.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’ll leave my keys with you,

259
00:14:58.772 --> 00:15:01.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so leave them
in the mailbox downstairs when you go out.

260
00:15:04.236 --> 00:15:06.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Sorry to leave you alone.</i>

261
00:15:08.198 --> 00:15:11.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>But I just couldn’t make it</i>
<i>through the night tonight.</i>

262
00:15:12.077 --> 00:15:15.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bye, Takumi. I’ll come pick you up
tomorrow morning at ten.

263
00:15:15.831 --> 00:15:18.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don’t you dare leave your room until then.

264
00:15:18.083 --> 00:15:20.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
