00:15:46.779 --> 00:15:48.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>The price on the meter</i>
<i>is getting pretty high.</i>

271
00:15:48.989 --> 00:15:52.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>By the time I get there, it could be</i>
<i>as high as my wages for tomorrow.</i>

272
00:15:54.244 --> 00:15:56.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ROOM 2015. JUST SO YOU KNOW,
IT’S NOT A SUITE.

273
00:15:56.413 --> 00:15:58.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
THOSE ARE SPECIAL
FOR FIRST AND LAST STAYS ONLY.

274
00:16:04.338 --> 00:16:06.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Which means this isn’t</i>
<i>the last time, right?</i>

275
00:16:07.800 --> 00:16:10.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Nobu, you were more popular
than me tonight.

276
00:16:11.053 --> 00:16:14.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
