278
00:16:16.266 --> 00:16:17.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
How about another drink
somewhere around here?

279
00:16:18.060 --> 00:16:20.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No thank you.
I have to go to work tomorrow.

280
00:16:20.688 --> 00:16:24.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
